<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Compte bloqué</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            color: #1f2937;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #6b7280;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #ffffff;
            background-color: #4f46e5;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #4338ca;
        }

        .logo {
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
            height: 50px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="https://i.goopics.net/vmzwmf.png" alt="InformaCart" class="logo">
            <h2 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #1f2937; margin-top: 20px">Compte bloqué</h2>
        </div>
        <p style="text-align: center; color: #1f2937">Bonjour {{ firstname }},</p>
        <p style="text-align: center; color: #1f2937">Votre compte a été verrouillé en raison de plusieurs tentatives de connexion échouées.</p>
        <p style="text-align: center; color: #1f2937">Veuillez réessayer dans {{ lockDuration }}.</p>
        <p style="text-align: center; color: #1f2937">Merci de votre compréhension.</p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p style="color: #6b7280">©2024 InformaCart. Tous droits réservés.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
